thread.title: Vanessa Bershatsky

author: Vanessa Bershatsky
title: Vanessa Bershatsky
text:
I was so excited to try all these kit kat flavors that I have been watching other Vloggers savor for months! This box was worth it because most of these kit kat bars are unavailable in my area.
I did receive the box with a broken seal and contacted customer service to verify that I had received everything. Their quick response was much appreciated and I was relieved that my Bokksu box was complete!
I am very much looking forward to next month's delivery!
